  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "When running large numbers of validators handled via external signer (web3signer), at each epoch transition VC will requests several `signAggregationSlot` (needed to calculate `isAggregate`) that could compete with `createRandaoReveal` needed to call block production for the first slot of the epoch.\r\n\r\nIdeally we could precompute some signatures in advance to leave more capacity for the time-sensitive duty signature.\r\n\r\nWe could even precompute `createRandaoReveal` a bit early to call createUnsignedBlock removing signing delay.",
